snippet.title: Amber Heard's Friend Afraid the Actress Would Die During Alleged Johnny Depp Abuse
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's Friend Afraid the Actress Would Die During Alleged Johnny Depp Abuse..
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjDtGelMNkllI5S22oO_aA?sub_confirmation=1
 Raquel Pennington claims the 'Aquaman' star still has scars on her arms from alleged Johnny Depp abuse but admits she never personally saw the actor hit her.   Jul 25, 2020   AceShowbiz - A close friend of actress Amber Heard's became really scared for the "Aquaman" star's life after an alleged Johnny Depp attack during a March, 2015 fight she told a court in London.    Raquel Pennington became the latest eye witness to Depp's reported abuse to take the stand at his ongoing libel trial against The Sun newspaper on Friday (24Jul20), and testified she feared the actor would kill her pal.         Pennington insisted Heard "still has scars on her arms from this incident" in her witness statement, but while speaking in London's High Court via video link from Los Angeles, she confessed she had never actually seen Depp hit Heard.    Heard previously testified she thought her then-husband was going to kill her during a "three-day hostage situation" at their rented home in Australia while Depp ...
